com.gtu.hw3

Class LinkedArrayList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<T>
        • com.gtu.hw3.LinkedArrayList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of elements held in this linked array list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>

    public class LinkedArrayList<T>
extends java.util.AbstractList<T>
implements java.util.List<T>
    Linked array list class that implements List interface and extends AbstractList class. This class holds data type T in nodes which has an array in it and all nodes are linked together with each node pointing the next and previous node.
    Since:
    2020-04-02
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Berke Belgin
    See Also:
    List, AbstractList
